<BR>&nbsp;</font>
<P><font face="Times New Roman">160</font>
<P><font face="Times New Roman">about that.</font>
<P><font face="Times New Roman"><B>A.</B> I have to ask you a question. Before this law was passed what stopped them from doing it?</font>
